 "Type of currency and per night amount of the rentals";            ?>        </p>         <!-- <p>            <?php            if ($this->lang->line('Fornewlistings') != '') {                echo stripslashes($this->lang->line('Fornewlistings'));            } else                echo "For new listings with no reviews, its important to set a competitive price. Once you get your first booking and review, you can raise your price!";            ?>        </p>        <p><strong>                <?php                if ($this->lang->line('Thesuggestednightly') != '') {                    echo stripslashes($this->lang->line('Thesuggestednightly'));                } else                    echo "The suggested nightly price tip is based on:";                ?>            </strong>        <p>            <?php            if ($this->lang->line('Seasonaltravel') != '') {                echo stripslashes($this->lang->line('Seasonaltravel'));            } else                echo "Seasonal travel demand in your area.";            ?></p>        <p>            <?php            if ($this->lang->line('Themediannightly') != '') {                echo stripslashes($this->lang->line('Themediannightly'));            } else                echo "The median nightly price of recent bookings in your city.";            ?></p> -->    </div>    <i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o toggleNotes" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><!-- Script to validate price per night --><script type="text/javascript">    function validate_price() {         $('.loading').show();        var price = $("#price_field");        var curren_select = $('#curren_select').val();        var price_exp = /^\d{0,}(\.\d{0,2})?$/;        if (price.val() == "") {             $('.loading').hide();            document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "block";            document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "<?php  if ($this->lang->line('err_price_per_night') != '') {                echo stripslashes($this->lang->line('err_price_per_night'));            } else {                echo "Please enter price per night";            } ?>";            setTimeout(function () {                document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "";                document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "none";            }, 2000);            price.focus();            return false;        }        else if (!price.val().match(price_exp)) {             $('.loading').hide();            document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "block";            document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "<?php  if ($this->lang->line('err_valid_price') != '') {                echo stripslashes($this->lang->line('err_valid_price'));            } else {                echo "Please enter valid price";            } ?>";            setTimeout(function () {                document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "";                document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "none";            }, 2000);            price.focus();            return false;        }         else if (curren_select == 0) {            $('.loading').hide();            document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "block";            document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "<?php  if ($this->lang->line('select_currency') != '') {                echo stripslashes($this->lang->line('select_currency'));            } else {                echo "Please Select Currency";            } ?>";            setTimeout(function () {                document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "";                document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "none";            }, 2000);                       return false;         }        else {            document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "none";            document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "";        }    }</script><script type="text/javascript">    /*function to check float values*/    function validateFloatKeyPress(el, evt) {        var charCode = (evt.which) ? evt.which : event.keyCode;        var number = el.value.split('.');        if (charCode != 46 && charCode > 31 && (charCode < 48 || charCode > 57)) {            return false;        }        /*just one dot*/        if (number.length > 1 && charCode == 46) {            return false;        }        /*get the carat position*/        var caratPos = getSelectionStart(el);        var dotPos = el.value.indexOf(".");        if (caratPos > dotPos && dotPos > -1 && (number[1].length > 1)) {            document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "block";            document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "After decimel two digits only allowed!";            setTimeout(function () {                document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "";                document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "none";            }, 2000);            return false;            price.focus();        }        else {            document.getElementById("errordisplay").style.display = "none";            document.getElementById("danger").innerHTML = "";        }        return true;    }    function getSelectionStart(o) {        if (o.createTextRange) {            var r = document.selection.createRange().duplicate()            r.moveEnd('character', o.value.length)            if (r.text == '') return o.value.length            return o.value.lastIndexOf(r.text)        } else return o.selectionStart    }    $("#price_field").on('keyup', function (e) {        var val = $(this).val();        if (val.match(/[^0-9.\s]/g)) {            document.getElementById("price_field_error").style.display = "inline";            $("#price_field").focus();            $("#price_field_error").fadeOut(5000);            $(this).val(val.replace(/[^a-zA-Z\s]/g, ''));        }    });</script>